<section name="Powered By - pow2ACL">

  <subsection name="Description">
    <p>
      <a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/pow2acl" target="_new">pow2ACL</a> 
	  gives access control list facility to web applications.
      It provides a JSP tag library and custom 
      <a href="http://jakarta.apache.org/struts" target="_new">Struts</a> action classes.
    </p>
  </subsection>

